Installation Instructions
*************************

What you need installed
***********************

cmake-2.4 (this is the build system used)
gtk+-2
libglade-2
gmodule-2
gtkglext-1.0
OpenCascade6.2
boost C++ libraries (only use shared_ptr.hpp)


Compile and run instructions
****************************

1. set CASROOT environment variable
2. run cmake
3. run make
4. execute ark3d


Here's an example of the build and run process on my machine
**********************************************

export CASROOT=~/opencascade-6.2/ros
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH=/opt/OpenCASCADE-6.2/lib
cmake .
make
./src/Interface/ark3d



